text: Miss Caribbean UK 2016, the 3rd edition of the Miss Caribbean UK pageant, was held on 3 December 2016 at the Broadway Theatre in Catford London, UK. Amy Harris-Willock crowned her successor, the model, Jodie Hodgson, who was representing Barbados. Thirteen contestants competed for the crown. ==References== ==External links== * "Official Souvenir Brochure 2016". Miss Caribbean UK. Retrieved 19 December 2015. 2016
